UWTN = TL Modifier + Pop Code Modifier

WTN = UWTN + Port Modifier

Trade Codes

- Ag = Agricultural. Producer of food stuffs. Earthlike world with Thin-Dense atmosphere, hydrosphere 35-84% and a population of 5000-99999
- As = Asteroid Belt. Many smaller wordlets in place of a single world
- Ba = Barren World. No population, government, or law but is colonizeable.
- De = Desert World. No water. A desert world has a Thin-Dense atmosphere and hydrosphere of 4% or less
- Ex = Extreme. Inhopistable planet. As, De, Fl, Ic, Va are all Extreme
- Eo = Exotic Ocean. Oceans composed of fluids other than water. Exotic or Corrosive Atmosphere and hydrosphere >5%
- Hi = High Population. Population 250k +
- Ic = Ice Capped. Hydrographics containerd in polar ice caps. 
- In = Industrial. heavy industry 
- Lo = Low Population. < 500
- Na = Non-Agricultural. <35% surface water pop 6+
- Po = Poor. Low grade living conditions. 
- Ri = Rich. High grade living condition
- Va = Vacuum World. No atmosphere
- Wa = Water World. >94% surface water

Traffic Classification

Main Route. Worls on the Main Route in a sector

Feeder Route. Worlds on Feeder Routes in a sector.

Backwater. Worlds are on the Minor routes

Frontier. Worlds are not on any routes.

