| Poor          | x0.8                           |
| Extreme       | x0.8                           |
| Nonindustrial | x0.8                           |

Planet GDP is base Per capita  * Population

So a population 500 TL 8 Poor world is GDP 3200ch


Between two worlds 

1. WTCM World Trade Classification Modifier

Starts at 0

One world is Ag and the other is Ex or Na: +0.5

One world is In and the other is Ni +0.5

Worlds do not share the same political allegiance: -0.5

2. Determine Distance Modifier

| Distance Modifier | Distance pc |
| ----------------- | ----------- |
| 0-1               | 0           |
| 2                 | 0.5         |
| 3-5               | 1           |
| 6-9               | 1.5         |
| 10-19             | 2           |
| 20-29             | 2.5         |
| 30-59             | 3           |
| 60-99             | 3.5         |
| 100-199           | 4           |
| 200-299           | 4.5         |
| 300-599           | 5           |
| 600-999           | 5.5         |
| 1000              | 6           |

3. Calculate Bilateral Trade Number BTN\

BTN = WTN World 1 + WTN WOrld 2 + WTCM - Distance Modifier

4. Interpret Results

BTN can be translated into chits and tons of cargo using the following

| BTN  | Chits/Year | Tons/Year | Tons/Week | Tons/Day  |
| ---- | ---------- | --------- | --------- | --------- |
| 0    | 0-5        | 0         | 0         | 0         |
| 0.5  | 5-10       | 0         | 0         | 0         |
| 1    | 10-50      | 0         | 0         | 0         |
| 1.5  | 50-100     | 0         | 0         | 0         |
| 2    | 100-500    | 0         | 0         | 0         |
| 2.5  | 500-1k     | 0         | 0         | 0         |
| 3    | 1k-5k      | 0         | 0         | 0         |
| 3.5  | 5k-10k     | 0         | 0         | 0         |
| 4    | 10k-50k    | 0-5       | 0         | 0         |
| 4.5  | 50k-100k   | 5-10      | 0         | 0         |
| 5    | 100k-500k  | 10-50     | 0         | 0         |
| 5.5  | 500k-1m    | 50-100    | 0-5       | 0         |
| 6    | 1m-5m      | 100-500   | 5-10      | 0         |
| 6.5  | 5m-10m     | 500-1k    | 10-50     | 0-5       |
| 7    | 10m-50m    | 1k-5k     | 50-100    | 5-10      |
| 7.5  | 50m-100m   | 5k-10k    | 100-500   | 10-50     |
| 8    | 100m-500m  | 10k-50k   | 500-1k    | 10-50     |
| 8.5  | 500m-1g    | 50k-100k  | 1k-5k     | 50-100    |
| 9    | 1g-5g      | 100k-500k | 5k-10k    | 100-500   |
| 9.5  | 5g-10g     | 500k-1m   | 10k-50k   | 500-1k    |
| 10   | 10g-50g    | 1m-5m     | 50-100k   | 1k-5k     |
| 10.5 | 50g-100g   | 5m-10m    | 100k-500k | 5k-10k    |
| 11   | 100g-500g  | 10m-50m   | 500k-1m   | 10k-50k   |
| 11.5 | 500g-1t    | 50m-100m  | 1m-5m     | 50k-100k  |
| 12   | 1t+        | 100m-500m | 5m-10m    | 100k-500k |


Modify BTN for distance

| Distance | BTN Mod |
| -------- | ------- |
| <50      | 0       |
| 50-99    | -0.5    |
| 100-499  | -1      |
| 500-999  | -1.5    |
| 1000+    | -2      |

To get the final value ranges beginning with 1 roll 1d5 rerolling 1s for the first digit and 1d4 for the others

Ranges beginning with 5 roll 1d6+4 for the first digit and 1d4 for the others


